" Commenting
" comma-1 insert "!" commenting
nnoremap <leader>1 :norm i!<cr>
vnoremap <leader>1 :norm i!<cr>

" comma-' insert """ commenting
nnoremap <leader>' :norm i"<cr>
vnoremap <leader>' :norm i"<cr>

" comma-3 insert "#" commenting
